Package main

Class GameWindow

java.lang.Object
main.GameWindow
Direct Known Subclasses:
BattleWindow, EnvironmentWindow, MainWindow, MenuWindow, MonJoinsWindow, ShopMenu
public abstract class GameWindow extends Object
An abstract class which every class that creates a Window using Java Swing will extend, contains methods reused by each of this subclasses
